{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_01","textHome":"如果，你是神滨的魔法少女的话，我必将手里@的佩剑染红。在你面前的是煌里光。PRO@MISED BLOOD引以为傲的三姐妹@的随从。顺便，你要不是神滨魔法少女的还@请早点告诉我。我得诚心诚意地向你道歉才@行。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_17","textHome":"但凡有什么感到困扰的事，请随时将我视作依@靠。辅助、支持所信赖的人，对我来说事不@会腻的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_18","textHome":"侍奉他人的喜悦。如今，我渐渐通过三姐妹感@受到了。如此，能够信赖的人变多，我感到@很幸福"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_19","textHome":"这样一来，光之部队或许会变得更多"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_20","textHome":"我们会让这出复仇剧以good end结尾"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_21","textHome":"这样一来，我就获得了能够守护珍视之人的力@量。要是以后能帮到二木市的所有魔法少女@就好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_22","textHome":"如果问我要服从到什么程度、奉献到什么程度@，我会毫不犹豫地回答，直到耗尽这条性命@。既然这条命不为了某个人便无法燃烧，那@我愿作为那个人最强的盾和矛，燃尽这条性@命"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_23","textHome":"即便自己所信赖的人走在了错误地道路上，我@也会和此人同行，做好奔赴死地的决心。当@然去纠正错误也当是我的义务，但仍不回头@的话，我会不论黑白地跟随的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_24","textHome":"做饭、洗衣、打扫、跑腿、擦鞋。今天也要为@了支持三姐妹，努力做好随从的工作。好了@，首先得从叫次女起床开始"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_25","textHome":"哎，用平底锅把次女给敲醒了之后，被她好生@发了一通火。我还以为这是个自古以来的惯@例…。用中式炒菜锅的话应该可以吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_26","textHome":"争斗会从夜里开始，趁白天得把武器给好好地@打磨。当然，保证身体与内心的刀刃的锋利@是基本"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_02","textHome":"把本煌里光叫出来，看样子你挺上道啊。要问@为什么的话，因为我从头到脚都是个随从。@需要任何支援都请交给我"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_27","textHome":"夜晚来临之前会稍微做一些按摩哦。我的指压@可是会酥麻到心脏去的。不管是肩膀还是腰@都可以让我来按摩哦"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_28","textHome":"啊——对不起…今天的我已经燃料不足了…。@做了太多的事情，剩下的时间就让我懒洋洋@地呆着吧…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200,"motion":300}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_29","textHome":"像这样空出来的时间，我会进行据点地打扫。@我想让这里成为大家能舒适呆着地地方。这@也是我的任务。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_30","textHome":"察觉到了敌人的气息！虽然还只是微弱的反应@，但有是魔法少女的可能性。得赶紧做准备@发动奇袭！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_31","textHome":"哈——…。像公寓一样叠了不知道多少层的结@界吗…。虽然有印象见过，但之前并不知道@是一个会制造复制品的危险的地方"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_32","textHome":"对我们二木市的魔法少女而言，集团战这种事@情可谓稀松平常。我们可不至于弱到光凭威@压就能把我们压倒的程度"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_33","textHome":"嗯——，将来我也想从事能够辅助谁的工作…@。果然还是政治家的秘书之类的？不对，果@然还是保镖更适合我"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_34","textHome":"虽然我很擅长做菜，但一个人的话就提不起劲@来做。不和谁一起的话，经常会很随便地做@个洋芋片就应付了…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":1}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_35","textHome":"果然…果然还是想要…！…马！说到随从，就@必须是马吧？像这样，飒爽地驱驰着，不帅@吗"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_042.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_36","textHome":"安静点。在考试中不及格的话，会没法在学生@会里面呆下去的。我、我可绝不能因此和长@女说拜拜的"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_03","textHome":"以前的我是对什么都很快会腻的那类"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_37","textHome":"哇——！哎呀——，这只小狗可真是毛绒绒啊@——！你是哪里的毛绒绒呀？毛绒绒！毛绒@绒！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":400}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_38","textHome":"糟了！真的糟了！长女的愤怒达到沸点了！赶@紧递冰糕给她冷静一下才行…！哦对，可以@的话买吧哩吧哩君最好！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_39","textHome":"大量采购碳酸饮料的次女…想要VR套装的三@女…。团体的资金可不是个人的东西啊…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":102200,"motion":300}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_40","textHome":"你会去思考，父母想要自己成为怎样的人吗…@？而我并没有成长为父母所期望的那样…。@这让我时常，感到有些担心"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102200,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":102200}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":102200,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1022_00_41","textHome":"今天的话，干脆看电视打发时间去好了…。嗯@…呜哇！你什么时候在的!?我一个人的时@候会在工作状态外，来了要跟我说一声！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.js